0:08:57.806,000 --> 0:09:,000
and I have to say that I do have particularly good ones.

211
0:09:01.202,000 --> 0:09:03,000
Now, I'm not going to share them with you,

212
0:09:03.204,000 --> 0:09:04,000
but this is the place that most people

213
0:09:05.183,000 --> 0:09:06,000
have looked for pheromones.

214
0:09:06.92,000 --> 0:09:07,000
There is one good reason,

215
0:09:08.423,000 --> 0:09:11,000
which is, the great apes have armpits

216
0:09:11.827,000 --> 0:09:13,000
as their unique characteristic.

217
0:09:14.155,000 --> 0:09:16,000
The other primates have scent glands

218
0:09:16.556,000 --> 0:09:17,000
in other parts of the body.

219
0:09:18.386,000 --> 0:09:2,000
The great apes have these armpits

220
0:09:20.74,000 --> 0:09:22,000
full of secretory glands

221
0:09:22.957,000 --> 0:09:24,000
producing smells all the time,

222
0:09:25.298,000 --> 0:09:28,000
enormous numbers of molecules.

223
0:09:28.998,000 --> 0:09:29,000
When they're secreted from the glands,

224
0:09:30.701,000 --> 0:09:32,000
