0:10:35.184,000 --> 0:10:39,000
So it doesn't apply to 20 percent of the world.

251
0:10:39.691,000 --> 0:10:42,000
So what should we be doing

252
0:10:42.693,000 --> 0:10:45,000
in our search for human pheromones?

253
0:10:45.746,000 --> 0:10:47,000
